verbose_text: Hence, the study was based on the measurement of existing levels of water quality parameters, including pH, dissolved oxygen (DO), total alkalinity (TA), electrical conductivity (EC), total dissolved solids (TDS), and chloride (Cl -), and selected metals (Ca, Cd, Co, Cr, Cu, Fe, K, Li, Mg, Mn, Na, Ni, Pb, Sr, and Zn) in surface water in summer and winter from Mangla Lake.
